msgstr "Employés"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Employees** centralizes :doc:`personnel files <employees/"
"new_employee>`, employment :doc:`contracts <payroll/contracts>`, "
"and :doc:`departmental hierarchies <employees/departments>` in one system. "
"In addition, each employee record tracks :doc:`certifications <employees/"
"certifications>` and :doc:`training <employees/learning>`, "
"earned :doc:`badges <employees/badges>`, and all assigned :doc:`equipment "
"<employees/equipment>`. Customizable :doc:`onboarding <employees/"
"onboarding>` and :doc:`offboarding <employees/offboarding>` programs ensure "
"all employees are trained and ready for work, and all required steps are "
"taken when they leave."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Employés** centralise les :doc:`dossiers du personnel <employees/"
"new_employee>`, les :doc:`contrats <payroll/contracts>` de travail et "
"les :doc:`hiérarchies départementales <employees/departments>` dans un seul "
"système. De plus, chaque fiche employé suit les :doc:`certifications "
"<employees/certifications>` et la :doc:`formation <employees/learning>`, "
"les :doc:`badges <employees/badges>` obtenus et tout l':doc:`équipement "
"<employees/equipment>` attribué. Des programmes d':doc:`intégration "
"<employees/onboarding>` et de :doc:`départ <employees/offboarding>` "
"personnalisables garantissent que tous les employés sont formés et prêts à "
"travailler, et que toutes les étapes requises sont suivies lors de leur "
"départ."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:16
msgid ""
"Properly configuring the settings in the **Employees** app ensures the "
"dashboard shows each employee's real-time attendance and work location—data "
"that drives payroll accuracy, capacity planning, and compliance reporting."
msgstr ""
"Configurer correctement les paramètres de l'application **Employés** "
"garantit que le tableau de bord affiche la présence en temps réel et le lieu "
"de travail de chaque employé, données qui alimentent la précision de la "
"paie, la planification des capacités et les rapports de conformité."

